{"tid":986362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭芭蕾男舞者歧視同志、肥胖者　巴黎歌劇院撤邀請","createTime":"2019-01-18T11:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T09:47:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46b87741e231899008179da0b88b5899dcf26a95","tid":986362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"來自烏克蘭29歲的芭蕾男舞者波路寧（Sergei Polunin），擁有精湛舞技的他，原本被巴黎歌劇院芭蕾舞團邀請在下月的《天鵝湖》演出，卻因他歧視同性戀、肥胖者等等脫序的言論，決定撤回對他的邀請。<br />\n<br />\n波路寧在13歲時就展現他驚人的才華，被倫敦皇家芭蕾舞學校喻為天才，擁有完美的身段與精湛的芭蕾舞技，被稱作為「芭蕾壞男孩」。出身於烏克蘭的波路寧是普丁的狂熱支持者，甚至在胸前刺了他的頭像。<br />\n<br />\n據《衛報》報導，波路寧原被邀請在巴黎歌劇院芭蕾舞團2月份的天鵝湖演出中飾演齊格菲王子。沒想到上週末邀請被撤回，傳出是因為他多次在社群媒體上發表不當言論。<br />\n<br />\n波路寧曾在Instagram上寫道「給所有跳芭蕾的男人，舞台上已經有一位芭蕾女伶，不需要有2位。男人就應該像個男人，女人就該像個女人。陽性和陰性的力量創造平衡，這就是為何你們有蛋蛋。」他甚至將注意力放到過重的人身上，曾發文表示，「當你看到胖子時就打他們耳光，這可以幫助他們並鼓勵他們減掉一些脂肪。」該貼文隨即又被刪除。"},{"pid":"77b124ab26ce25061cb3e73a57b27d955f2e1e8b","tid":986362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20190117edi017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20190117edi017&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b2a9a6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20190117edi017</a>"},{"pid":"4119bd2a73ef59ddb9c2a0af7a816bcb48761b44","tid":986362,"uid":126866,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"啲死基佬真係麻煩"},{"pid":"d36599c40aa35252349ea221dbb29ac543b99aac","tid":986362,"uid":150706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4119bd2a73ef59ddb9c2a0af7a816bcb48761b44","tid":986362,"uid":126866,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"啲死基佬真係麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"可能係肥婆投訴"},{"pid":"f7139d546d8c043862ef403f9430f55c100fb943","tid":986362,"uid":43842,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"歧視人歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正一法西斯"},{"pid":"2077e18258bf72120799227d6c9265ab40e3d8eb","tid":986362,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"基佬同肥佬都好難頂"},{"pid":"ac592b837703418514378706c0ef58cc0376c4df","tid":986362,"uid":21699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d108f0a2c0c27ae05575cdbdb298efd83352c3","tid":986362,"uid":36857,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"東歐國家係白人最後希望"},{"pid":"e8fe3cf51e4bd310f6ea65f9499447c45bd5f6cc","tid":986362,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d108f0a2c0c27ae05575cdbdb298efd83352c3","tid":986362,"uid":36857,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"東歐國家係白人最後希望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"不如話俄佬"},{"pid":"789f65acdb180f4f8c8967f02bc7c89a99264a05","tid":986362,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac592b837703418514378706c0ef58cc0376c4df","tid":986362,"uid":21699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"佢嗰句似歧視乸型多過gay"},{"pid":"c610f4665884415a0e100a4bcc4b6dc882b709fe","tid":986362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}